item.title: Happy Birthday to us, Happy Birthday to us!
item.description: Well it's our first birthday, how time flies when you're having fun.It's hard for us to get our tiny brains around just how far we've come in such a short period of time. We put the site together and grabbed our @LeedsDevops twitter handle and we were off... We are indebted to those who have supported us throughout the year from local groups and business' and we've had some great meetups.
